        <heading>Section </heading>
        <content>
          <p>CHAPTER 4.  JURY TRIALS PROHIBITED; TRANSFER
TO DISTRICT COURT
Art. 4871.  Jury trial prohibited
There shall be no trial by jury in any case in a parish court, city court, or justice of the peace court.</p>
        </content>
